But does it bollocks. Not compared
to how people matter.

937
01:36:47,647 --> 01:36:50,878
Us winning this trophy won't mean
bugger all to most people.

938
01:36:51,047 --> 01:36:53,959
But us refusing it, like what
we're going to do now...

939
01:36:54,367 --> 01:36:56,005
well then it becomes news,
doesn't it?

940
01:36:58,487 --> 01:36:59,886
You see what I mean.

941
01:37:00,247 --> 01:37:02,681
That way I’ll not just be talking
to myself, will l?

942
01:37:03,007 --> 01:37:05,646
Because over the last ten years,
this bloody government...

943
01:37:05,807 --> 01:37:08,685
has systematically destroyed
an entire industry.

944
01:37:09,007 --> 01:37:11,840
Our industry. And not just our
industry.

945
01:37:12,007 --> 01:37:14,885
Our communities, our homes,
our lives.

946
01:37:15,247 --> 01:37:18,683
AII in the name of progress and
for a few lousy bob.

947
01:37:19,247 --> 01:37:22,319
I’ll tell you something else you
might not know. A fortnight ago...

948
01:37:22,727 --> 01:37:24,479
this band's pit were closed.

949
01:37:24,647 --> 01:37:28,083
Another thousand men Lost their jobs.
And that's not all they lost.

950
01:37:28,407 --> 01:37:31,046
Most of them Lost the will to win
a while ago.

951
01:37:31,327 --> 01:37:33,522
A few of them even lost
the will to fight.

952
01:37:33,687 --> 01:37:34,722
But...

953
01:37:36,127 --> 01:37:40,484
When it comes to losing the will
to live, to breathe...

954
01:37:41,847 --> 01:37:43,075
point is...

955
01:37:44,167 --> 01:37:46,886
if this lot were seals or whales,
you'd be up in bloody arms.

956
01:37:47,047 --> 01:37:50,881
But they're not. They’re just
ordinary, common or garden...

957
01:37:51,047 --> 01:37:54,562
honest, decent human beings.
And not one of them...

958
01:37:55,087 --> 01:37:57,362
with an ounce
of bloody hope Left.

959
01:38:00,767 --> 01:38:03,156
They can knock out
a bloody good tune.

960
01:38:04,047 --> 01:38:06,163
But what the fuck
does that matter?

961
01:38:17,127 --> 01:38:20,005
Now I'm going to take my boys
out onto the town.

962
01:38:21,287 --> 01:38:22,481
