963
01:39:04,287 --> 01:39:06,847
-Are you coming back, Sand?
-I dunno.

964
01:39:07,967 --> 01:39:09,685
I’ve got a chair now.

965
01:39:10,567 --> 01:39:12,956
I’ve no frigging house,
but I’ve got a chair.

966
01:39:13,487 --> 01:39:15,842
Well, sort of a chair.

967
01:39:16,127 --> 01:39:18,083
