968
01:39:22,007 --> 01:39:23,076
All right?

969
01:39:24,367 --> 01:39:25,846
Is that a thank you?

970
01:39:26,527 --> 01:39:28,085
More than that.

971
01:39:28,247 --> 01:39:30,317
